# Zathura document viewer config.

set statusbar-h-padding 0
set statusbar-v-padding 0
set page-padding 1
set selection-clipboard clipboard
set recolor 1
set recolor-keephue 1

# KEYBINDS
## Document Navigation
map j navigate next
map <Down> navigate next

map k navigate previous
map <Up> navigate previous

map h navigate page-top
map <Left> navigate page-top

map l navigate page-bottom
map <Right> navigate page-bottom


## Page Scrolling
map u scroll full-up
map d scroll full-down

map U scroll half-up
map D scroll half-down

map J scroll down
map <S-Down> scroll down

map K scroll up
map <S-Up> scroll up

map H scroll left
map <S-Left> scroll left

map L scroll right
map <S-Right> scroll right


## View Modifications
map r rotate
map i recolor
map 0 zoom default
map 2 toggle_page_mode


## Modes
map 1 toggle_presentation
map [presentation] 1 toggle_presentation
map [presentation] 2 toggle_page_mode

map 3 toggle_fullscreen
map [fullscreen] 3 toggle_fullscreen
map [fullscreen] 2 toggle_page_mode

map 9 toggle_index
map [index] 9 toggle_index
map [index] 2 toggle_page_mode


## Misc
map R reload
map p print
